This PR duplicates the `polaris_ranger_xp900` pull request. In the future, wait for the first pull request to be approved before creating a new PR. Alternatively, decline the first PR and create new PR with the additions. 

This PR should not be merged until the `polaris_ranger_xp900` is merged, and you'll have to make sure all changes are consistent between the two pull requests.
